0of%20the%20costs.%20So%20I%20went%20over%20and%20thanked%20them%20for%20all%20their%20hard%20work%20but%20let%20them%20know%20we%20didn't%20have%20the%20money%20(or%20interest)%20to%20keep%20a%20garden%20on%20our%20half%20of%20the%20yard%2C%20so%20while%20we%20wouldn't%20charge%20them%20for%20using%20our%20space%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20be%20paying%20for%20it%20either.%20The%20conversation%20was%20awkward%2C%20but%20everything%20seemed%20fine.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20this%20spring%2C%20they%20have%20already%20been%20texting%20us%20pictures%20of%20the%20flowers%20they're%20buying%2C%20using%20our%20trashcans%20for%20yard%20waste%2C%20and%20even%20letting%20us%20know%20they%20used%20our%20hose%20to%20make%20the%20water%20bill%20fair.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20husband%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20going%20off%20on%20them%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20want%20bad%20blood%20with%20our%20neighbors.%20I%20feel%20like%20we've%20done%20everything%2C%20though%2C%20and%20at%20this%20point%2C%20they're%20being%20intentionally%20ignorant.%20What%20should%20I%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot-A-Gardener%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Not-A-Gardener%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELife%20has%20plenty%20of%20crossed%20wires%20and%20honest%20misunderstandings%2C%20but%20some%20things%20are%20simple.%20For%20instance%2C%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B%20is%20pretty%20straightforward.%20So%20if%20you%20tell%20someone%20%26quot%3Bno%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20they%20ignore%20it%2C%20they%20can't%20excuse%20themselves%20with%20an%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I%20didn't%20realize!%26quot%3B%20Because%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B%20simply%20doesn't%20leave%20room%20for%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20your%20previous%20nos%20were%20so%20polite%20they%20didn't%20catch%20it.%20Perhaps%20you%20smiled%2C%20congratulated%20them%20on%20their%20gardening%20skills%2C%20hemmed%20and%20ha