20terrifying%20because%20they%20have%20the%20power%20to%20make%20your%20life%20a%20nightmare%20by%20the%20sheer%20privilege%20of%20proximity.%20But%20is%20allowing%20them%20to%20continue%20manipulating%20you%20into%20a%20shared%20garden%20any%20better%20than%20dealing%20with%20the%20leaves%20they%20might%20vindictively%20blow%20into%20your%20yard%20every%20fall%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20write%20them%20a%20note.%20Yes%2C%20this%20is%20the%20height%20of%20passive-aggressive%20behavior.%20Still%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20have%20it%20in%20writing%20in%20case%20of%20future%20litigation%20so%20you%20can%20refer%20them%20back%20to%20the%20letter%20should%20they%20continue%20to%20violate%20your%20boundaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20I%20would%20write%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDear%20Neighbors%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe've%20noticed%20you%20are%20using%20our%20trash%20cans%20for%20yard%20waste%20and%20our%20hose%20for%20water.%20Combined%20with%20your%20repeated%20texts%20full%20of%20landscaping%20options%2C%20this%20has%20us%20worried%20that%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20when%20we%20told%20you%20we%20wouldn't%20participate%20in%20a%20shared%20garden%2C%20you%20didn't%20understand%20us.%20We%20want%20to%20be%20clear%3A%20By%20using%20our%20water%20and%20trash%20cans%2C%20you%20are%20involving%20us%20financially%20against%20our%20wishes.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20this%20is%20where%20you'll%20need%20to%20decide%20if%20your%20neighbors%20are%20actually%20ignorant%20or%20only%20pretending%20to%20be.%20If%20you%20think%20they%20genuinely%20mistook%20earlier%20%26quot%3Bno's%26quot%3B%20for%20tacit%20agreement%2C%20then%20you%20can%20give%20them%20another%20chance%20by%20ending%20your%20letter%20with%20a%20soft%20reminder%20like%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20don't%20mind%20if%20you%20use%20our%20property%20for%20your%20garden%2C%20but%20our%20involvement%20will%20need%20to%20end%20there.%20If%20that's%20too%20much%20work%20and%20money%20for%20you%