en%20will%20appear%20on%20a%20solo%20panel%20before%20the%20Senate%20Committee%20on%20Health%2C%20Education%2C%20Labor%2C%20and%20Pensions%20(HELP)%20in%20September%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanders.senate.gov%2Fpress-releases%2Fnews-sanders-announces-ceo-of-novo-nordisk-to-voluntarily-testify-before-help-committee%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20will%20focus%20on%20what%20was%20described%20in%20the%20press%20release%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Boutrageously%20high%20cost%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20drugs%2C%20which%20have%20soared%20in%20popularity%20over%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESanders%20thanked%20the%20CEO%20for%20volunteering%20to%20testify%20and%20said%20a%20vote%20on%20whether%20to%20subpoena%20Novo%20Nordisk%20to%20answer%20questions%20about%20the%20drugs'%20pricing%20would%20be%20canceled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20American%20people%20are%20sick%20and%20tired%20of%20paying%2C%20by%20far%2C%20the%20highest%20prices%20in%20the%20world%20for%20prescription%20drugs%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanders%20continued.%20%26quot%3BNovo%20Nordisk%20currently%20charges%20Americans%20with%20Type%202%20diabetes%20%24969%20a%20month%20for%20Ozempic%2C%20while%20this%20same%20exact%20drug%20can%20be%20purchased%20for%20just%20%24155%20in%20Canada%20and%20just%20%2459%20in%20Germany.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNovo%20Nordisk%20also%20charges%20Americans%20with%20obesity%20%241%2C349%20a%20month%20for%20Wegovy%2C%20while%20this%20same%20exact%20product%20can%20be%20purchased%20for%20just%20%24140%20in%20Germany%20and%20%2492%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20went%20on.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Committee%20looks%20forward%20to%20Mr.%20J%C3%B8rgensen%20explaining%20why%20Americans%20are%20paying%20up%20to%20ten%20or%2015%20times%20more%20for%20these%20medications%20than%20people%20in%20other%20countries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225677%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senate%20Health%2C%20Education%2C%20Labor%2C%20and%20Pensions%20Committee%20Chairman%20Bernie%20Sanders%20(I-VT)%20questions%20witnesses%20during%20a%20hearing%20about%20working%20hours%20in%20the%20Dirksen%20Senate%20Office%20Building%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20on%20March%2014%2C%202024%20in%20Washington%20DC.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f42ef53037f8e81750b106%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223784%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESenate%20Health%2C%20Education%2C%20Labor%2C%20and%20Pensions%20Committee%20Chairman%20Bernie%20Sanders%20(I-VT)%20questions%20witnesses%20during%20a%20hearing%20on%20March%2014%2C%202024%20in%20Washington%20DC.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESanders%20had%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanders.senate.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FLetter-from-Sen.-Bernard-Sanders-to-Novo-Nordisk.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewritten%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20J%C3%B8rgensen%20in%20April%20to%20inform%20him%20that%20HELP%20was%20investigating%20the%20costs%20of%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20development%20of%20the%20drugs%20deserved%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20credit%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20they%20could%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bgame%20changer%26quot%3B%20for%20US%20citizens%20dealing%20with%20obesity%20or%20diabetes.%20But%20he%20noted%20that%20the%20drugs%20were%20unaffordable%20to%20many%2C%20despite%20studies%20suggesting%20that%20they%20are%20priced%20far%20higher%20than%20their%20production%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20investigative%20analysis%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamanetworkopen%2Ffullarticle%2F2816824%3Futm_campaign%3DarticlePDF%26utm_medium%3DarticlePDFlink%26utm_source%3DarticlePDF%26utm_content%3Djamanetworkopen.2024.3474%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJAMA%20Network%20Open%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%