5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20birds%20that%20hit%20the%20A320%20were%20Canadian%20geese.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20has%20been%20maintained%20as%20it%20was%20after%20the%20investigation%2C%20including%20the%20dents%2C%20scrapes%2C%20and%20gaping%20holes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20see%20writing%20and%20numbers%20on%20the%20fuselage%20where%20investigators%20worked%20on%20the%20jet.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20wings%20were%20attached%20to%20the%20jet%2C%20but%20the%20flaps%20were%20wrecked%20from%20the%20crash.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wing%20damage%20on%20the%20A320.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c7f68764df161125a0ea6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221551%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWing%20damage%20on%20the%20left%20and%20right%20wings.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flaps%20were%20particularly%20important%20in%20the%20crash's%20success%20because%20Sully%20opted%20not%20to%20fully%20configure%20them%20for%20landing%2C%20per%20the%20NTSB.%20According%20to%20one%20of%20the%20museum%20signs%2C%20full%20flaps%20were%20part%20of%20Airbus'%20%26quot%3Boptimal%20aircraft%20configuration%26quot%3B%20for%20landing%20on%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20non-emergency%20landing%2C%20the%20flaps%20are%20fully%20deployed%20to%20increase%20lift%20at%20lower%20speeds%20as%20the%20plane%20descends.%20This%20balances%20out%20if%20you%20have%20thrust.%20However%2C%20without%20thrust%20on%20Flight%201549%2C%20Sully%20raised%20the%20flaps%20to%20prevent%20a%20stall%2C%20which%20could%20have%20led%20to%20an%20even%20faster%20descent%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20choice%20had%20to%20be%20made%20quickly%20because%20of%20the%20extreme%20time%20compression%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20NTSB%20testimony.%20%26quot%3BBy%20achieving%20Flaps%202%2C%20we%20had%20achieved%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20low-speed%20stall%20protection%20that%20we%20would've%20gotten%20at%20Flaps%203%2C%20but%20at%20less%20drag.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20two%20destroyed%20engines%20are%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20aircraft%2C%20and%20the%20auxiliary%20power%20unit%2C%20or%20APU%2C%20sits%20behind.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223705%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tail%20and%20APU%20are%20off%20the%20back.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c77a3e079049018193a1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222779%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20APU%20dislodged%20from%20the%20aircraft.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sully%20realized%20his%20engines%20were%20gone%2C%20he%20instinctively%20started%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faerospace.honeywell.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fabout-us%2Fblogs%2Fhudson-landing-still-a-miracle-a-decade-later%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHoneywell%3C%2Fa%3E-built%20APU.%20According%20to%20the%20manufacturer%2C%20the%20unit%20acted%20as%20backup%20power%20to%20control%20things%20like%20altitude%2C%20speed%2C%20and%20steering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NTSB%20concluded%20that%20by%20quickly%20turning%20on%20the%20APU%20before%20called%20for%20on%20the%20emergency%20checklist%2C%20%5BSully%5D%20significantly%20improved%20the%20outcome%20by%20providing%20electrical%20power%20to%20the%20airplane%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20information%20display%20next%20to%20the%20APU%20read%20at%20the%20museum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EVisitors%20cannot%20go%20inside%20the%20jet%2C%20but%20photos%20displayed%20show%20it%20looks%20like%20a%20regular%20aircraft%20cabin.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sully%20inside%20the%20Miracle%20on%20the%20Hudson%20A320.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c77c7e079049018193a36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESully%20inside%20the%20Miracle%20on%20the%20Hudson%20A320.%3Cp%3ETodd%20Sumlin%2FCharlotte%20Observer%2FTribune%20News%20Service%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPictures%20show%20the%20blue%20seats%20in%20the%20typical%20domestic%20layout.%20The%20cabin%20looks%20old%20and%20worn%2C%20but%20not%20as%20if%20it%20was%20in%20a%20serious%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20museum%2C%20the%20jet's%20interior%20is%20regularly%20checked%20for%20corrosion%2C%20considering%20it%20was%20submerged%20in%20water%20for%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20plane's%20underbelly%20took%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20impact%2C%20and%20I%20could%20see%20where%20it%20was%20torn%20off.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20jet%20from%20behind.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c7875764df161125a069f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20water%20around%20my%20feet%20immediately%2C%20and%20it%20was%20cold%2C%26quot%3B%20Flight%201549%20passenger%20Vicki%20Barnhardt%2C%20seat%2026C%2C%20said%20in%20the%20museum%20video.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NTSB%2C%20the%20aircraft%20was%20descending%20three%20times%20the%20rate%20at%20which%20the%20aviation%20industry%20said%20a%20water%20landing%20could%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20meant%20the%20aircraft's%20impact%20on%20the%20Hudson%20was%20greater%20than%20its%20design%20allowed%2C%20causing%20part%20of%20the%20frame%20to%20collapse%20and%20let%20water%20seep%20in.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20damage%20was%20extensive%2C%20but%20the%20aircraft%20was%20otherwise%20surprisingly%20intact.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tail%20number%20on%20the%20jet%20reads%3A%20N106US.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c7950ed9a404d829df4af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20tail%20number%20on%20the%20jet%20reads%20N106US.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESully%20had%20to%20land%20the%20aircraft%20at%20a%20specific%20angle%20to%20avoid%20flipping%20or%20fully%20breaking%20apart%20upon%20contact%20with%20the%20water.%20The%20museum%20said%20this%20included%20landing%20at%20an%2011-degree%20pitch%20with%20the%20wings%20level.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESully%20achieved%20this%20despite%20the%20high%20descent%20rate%20being%20beyond%20the%20accepted%20envelope%2C%20making%20the%20task%20that%20much%20more%20challenging%20and%20a%20testament%20to%20Sully's%20skill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%5BSkiles%5D%20began%20to%20call%20out%20to%20me%20airspeed%20and%20altitude%20as%20I%20was%20looking%20at%20the%20water%20ahead%20to%20help%20me%20judge%20that%20critical%20height%2C%26quot%3B%20Sully%20said%20in%20a%202019%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw6EblErBJqw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Inc%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20specific%20altitude%20at%20which%20to%20begin%20raising%20the%20nose%20for%20a%20successful%20water%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENext%20to%20the%20plane%20was%20a%20case%20of%20personal%20belongings%20donated%20by%20the%20crew%20and%20passengers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222487%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20display%20case%20below%20the%20giant%20video%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c7cf9764df161125a0be1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221865%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20display%20case%20sat%20below%20a%20large%20video%20screen.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EArtifacts%20like%20cushions%2C%20life%20jackets%2C%20seats%2C%20clothes%2C%20and%20even%20Sully%20and%20Skiles%20uniforms%20have%20been%20preserved%20and%20put%20on%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20was%20like%20a%20time%20capsule%20seeing%20the%20old%20Blackberry%20cell%20phone%20and%20MacBook%20Pro.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20display%20case%20with%20the%20cell%20hpone%20and%20laptop%20and%20other%20items%20like%20pillows%20and%20books%20and%20brushes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c7a1c764df161125a0859%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20display%20case%20had%20all%20sorts%20of%20donations%20from%20the%20passengers%20and%20crew.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20wallets%2C%20a%20finance%20book%2C%20and%20a%20fur%20coat%20among%20the%20inventory%20of%20random%20items%20that%20survived%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20most%20moving%20element%20of%20the%20exhibit%20was%20the%20film%20that%20played%20on%20a%20loop.%20It%20told%20the%20story%20of%20Flight%201549%20from%20takeoff%20to%20landing%20in%20the%20Hudson.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20video%20playing%20on%20a%20giant%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c7a75e079049018193c70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPassengers%2C%20like%20Brian%20Siegel%2C%20seat%208E%2C%20were%20interviewed%20for%20the%20video.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20short%20video%20has%20the%20air%20traffic%20control%20tapes%2C%20footage%20of%20the%20rescue%2C%20and%20testimony%20from%20passengers%2C%20investigators%2C%20and%20first%20responders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BUnable%2C%26quot%3B%20Sully%20famously%20told%20air%20traffic%20controller%20Patrick%20Harten%20when%20he%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20could%20make%20it%20back%20to%20LaGuardia.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20be%20in%20the%20Hudson.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20comments%20were%20raw%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20help%20but%20get%20emotional.%20The%20crew%20gets%20a%20lot%20of%20praise%2C%20but%20the%20passengers%20also%20showed%20incredible%20bravery.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22806%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miracle%20on%20the%20Hudson%20passengers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c7bb2e079049018193d3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22605%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMiracle%20on%20the%20Hudson%20passengers.%3Cp%3EMike%20Coppola%2FFilmMagic%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20lost%20power%20just%20a%20few%20thousand%20feet%20above%20NYC%2C%20and%20the%20passengers%20described%20their%20feelings%20as%20the%20city%20skyscrapers%20started%20rising%20above%20them%20and%20they%20descended%20into%20the%20Hudson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20flashed%20before%20me%20was%20the%20life%20that%20wasn't%20going%20to%20happen%2C%20the%20grandchildren%20I%20wouldn't%20see%20grow%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20passenger%20Beth%20McHugh%2C%20seat%2020C%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20imagine%20that%20fear%2C%20but%20seeing%20the%20hope%20after%20the%20fact%20is%20inspiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20gift%20of%20another%20day%2C%20another%20year%2C%20and%20if%20you%20look%20at%20it%20that%20way%2C%20another%20lifetime%2C%26quot%3B%20McHugh%20said%20later%20in%20the%20video.%20%26quot%3BBy%20some%20miracle%2C%20we%20get%20to%20have%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFlight%201549's%20rescue%20was%20swift%2C%20with%20boats%20and%20helicopters%20approaching%20within%20minutes.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221116%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miracle%20on%20the%20Hudson%20A320.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61ddf6991025b20018bb3e20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22704%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERescue%20boats%20at%20crash%20site.%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20accident%20happened%20in%20January%2C%20meaning%20the%20passengers%20survived%20the%20water%20landing%20but%20were%20still%20in%20danger%20of%20drowning%20or%20getting%20hypothermia%20in%20the%20frigid%20Hudson%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20walked%20out%20onto%20the%20wings%2C%20jumped%20into%20rafts%2C%20and%20some%20tried%20to%20swim%20to%20shore%20%E2%80%94%20anything%20to%20survive%20the%2038-degree%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20crew%20took%20out%2024%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20New%20York%20Waterways%20Captain%20Brittany%20Catanzard%20said%20in%20the%20video.%20%26quot%3BMy%20deckhands%20were%20literally%20grabbing%20them%20like%20fish%20and%20putting%20them%20onto%20the%20deck.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFlight%20attendants%20Donna%20Denta%2C%20Sheila%20Dail%2C%20and%20Doreen%20Welsh%20shouted%20commands%20as%20passengers%20braced%20for%20impact.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flight%20attendants%20and%20flight%20crew%20speaking.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c8262e07904901819443e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22695%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonna%20Dent%20(2nd%20L)%20speaks%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20with%20Sheila%20Dail%20(L)%2C%20Doreen%20Welsh(3rd%20L)%2C%20Jeffrey%20Skiles%20(3rd%20R)%2C%20Mayor%20Bloomberg%20(2nd%20R)%2C%20and%20Sully%20(R).%3Cp%3EMichael%20Nagle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20quick-acting%20flight%20attendants%20initiated%20the%20evacuation%20within%20seconds%20of%20landing%20and%2C%20alongside%20Sully%20and%20Skiles%2C%20were%20awarded%20the%20keys%20to%20the%20city%20by%20New%20York%20City%20Mayor%20Bloomberg%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp