tests%20over%20the%20war%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpro-palestine-protesters-arrested-stanford-university-occupying-presidents-office-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20nation%20grappled%20with%20the%20complexities%20of%20academic%20freedom%2C%20Gow%20was%20fighting%20a%20very%20different%20kind%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwisconsin-chancellor-fired-porn-onlyfans-first-amendment-free-speech-experts-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFirst%20Amendment%3C%2Fa%3E%20battle.%20And%20how%20the%20chancellor%20turned%20porn%20star%20winds%20up%20faring%20in%20his%20fight%20may%20tell%20us%20a%20lot%20about%20what%20kind%20of%20country%20we've%20become%20and%20just%20how%20far%20we're%20willing%20to%20extend%20the%20limits%20of%20free%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20early%20April%2C%20and%20I'm%20sitting%20at%20the%20dining%20table%20in%20Gow%20and%20Wilson's%20airy%20home%20a%20few%20miles%20from%20campus.%20Their%20snow-covered%20backyard%20is%20visible%20through%20a%20stately%20window%2C%20photos%20of%20their%20grandchildren%20perched%20on%20a%20nearby%20ledge.%20Before%20I%20arrived%2C%20they%20asked%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20watch%20them%20have%20sex%2C%20which%20they%20do%20five%20or%20six%20nights%20a%20week%2C%20usually%20just%20before%20having%20dinner.%20To%20my%20relief%2C%20they%20ultimately%20decided%20that%20doing%20it%20in%20front%20of%20me%20would%20be%20too%20weird.%20Instead%2C%20they%20suggest%20we%20watch%20them%20having%20sex%20on%20screen.%20As%20they%20sit%20beside%20me%20sipping%20white%20wine%2C%20Gow%20opens%20his%20laptop%20and%20cues%20up%20%26quot%3BJuicy%20Anniversary%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20third%20professionally%20produced%20porn%20they%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joe%20Gow%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66635a2ded9a404d829bd4d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222355%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBefore%20someone%20forwarded%20%26quot%3BJuicy%20Anniversary%26quot%3B%20to%20his%20boss%2C%20Gow%20was%20a%20beloved%20chancellor%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin.%3Cp%3ESimone%20Lueck%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGow%20and%20Wilson%20met%20at%20UW-La%20Crosse%20in%202006.%20He%20was%20a%20candidate%20for%20chancellor%3B%20she%20was%20on%20the%20hiring%20committee.%20Rumors%20swirled%20that%20the%20two%2C%20both%20married%2C%20were%20having%20an%20affair%2C%20an%20accusation%20they%20denied.%20Wilson%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20psychology%2C%20served%20as%20Gow's%20chief%20of%20staff%20for%20two%20years%20before%20becoming%20the%20head%20of%20what%20was%20then%20UW-Rock%20County.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20Wilson%20and%20her%20second%20husband%20divorced%20after%2020%20years%20of%20marriage.%20Shortly%20after%2C%20Gow%20ended%20his%20marriage%20of%2025%20years.%20The%20two%20say%20they%20began%20dating%20in%202013%2C%20bonding%20over%20their%20bad%20marriages%2C%20their%20veganism%2C%20and%20their%20desire%20for%20sexual%20adventure.%20They%20were%20married%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-san-francisco-worth-it-cost-of-living-negativity-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESan%20Francisco%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20a%20ceremony%20where%20they%20started%20on%20opposite%20sides%20of%20the%20Golden%20Gate%20Bridge%20and%20met%20in%20the%20middle.%20It%20made%20a%20BuzzFeed%20list%20of%20%26quot%3B32%20Incredibly%20Beautiful%20Elopements%20You%20Have%20to%20See.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20monogamy%20hadn't%20worked%20out%20for%20them%2C%20Gow%20and%20Wilson%20decided%20they%20were%20going%20to%20do%20things%20differently%20this%20time.%20First%20they%20tried%20a%20threesome%20with%20an%20ex-girlfriend%20of%20Wilson's%20(too%20awkward).%20Then%20they%20explored%20polyamory%20(too%20emotionally%20fraught).%20Finally%2C%20they%20tried%20hiring%20escorts%20(just%20right).%20They%20liked%20paying%20for%20a%20service%2C%20with%20no%20strings%20attached.%20But%20all%20the%20escorts%20were%20female%2C%20mainly%20because%20male%20escorts%20were%20hard%20to%20find%20in%20western%20Wisconsin.%20In%20search%20of%20a%20man%20for%20Wilson%2C%20Gow%20sought%20advice%20from%20his%20therapist%2C%20who%20suggested%20joining%20a%20swingers%20club.%20But%20they%20found%20that%20the%20other%20attendees%2C%20as%20Wilson%20puts%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Blacked%20hygiene.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Wilson%20and%20Gow%2C%20like%20most%20Americans%2C%20watch%20porn.%20Eventually%20they%20thought%3A%20Why%20not%20make%20our%20own%3F%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThey%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fbest-buy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBest%20Buy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20bought%20a%20Sony%20camcorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20connection%20to%20the%20porn%20industry%20began%20with%20a%20male%20stripper%20they%20paid%20to%20give%20them%20a%20private%20performance%20in%20their%20hotel%20room%20in%20Chicago%2C%20where%20they%20were%20attending%20the%20annual%20conference%20of%20the%20Higher%20Learning%20Commission.%20After%20the%20show%2C%20Gow%20says%2C%20the%20stripper%20was%20happy%20to%20get%20it%20on%20with%20Wilson%20for%20free%20while%20Gow%20filmed%20them.%20During%20a%20postcoital%20conversation%2C%20the%20couple%20shared%20that%20they%20were%20interested%20in%20making%20high-quality%20porn%20films%20of%20themselves.%20The%20stripper%20said%20there%20was%20another%20convention%20in%20town%20that%20might%20have%20what%20they%20were%20looking%20for.%20So%20after%20they%20were%20done%20with%20their%20panels%20on%20accreditation%20and%20assessment%20in%20higher%20education%2C%20Gow%20and%20Wilson%20visited%20the%20Exxxotica%20convention%2C%20looking%20to%20hire%20porn%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20their%20first%20shoot%2C%20the%20couple%20hired%20a%2021-year-old%20porn%20actor%20for%20about%20%241%2C000%20and%20took%20turns%20filming%20their%20sex%20with%20her.%20Then%20they%20spent%20%242%2C350%20to%20hire%20a%20porn%20studio%20%E2%80%94%20camera%20crew%2C%20makeup%2C%20and%20editing%20%E2%80%94%20to%20shoot%20them%20having%20sex%20on%20a%20professional%20set%20in%20a%20penthouse%20loft%20in%20downtown%20Los%20Angeles.%20It%20turned%20them%20on%20to%20be%20watched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPorn%20actors%20say%20it's%20fairly%20common%20for%20people%20to%20hire%20them%20to%20appear%20in%20private%20home%20videos.%20The%20industry%20%26quot%3Bfrowns%20upon%26quot%3B%20the%20practice%2C%20according%20to%20one%20veteran%2C%20viewing%20it%20as%20an%20unprofessional%20side%20hustle.%20But%20Gow%20and%20Wilson%20had%20no%20trouble%20hiring%20plenty%20of%20big%20names%20in%20the%20business%3A%20Gow's%20teenage%20crush%20Nina%20Hartley%2C%20young%20hunk%20Danny%20Mountain%2C%20newcomer%20India%20Summer%2C%20who'd%20had%20a%20career%20in%20finance.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20worked%20with%20people%20with%20degrees%20from%20MIT%2C%20USC%2C%20Cal%20Berkeley%2C%26quot%3B%20Gow%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222194%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carmen%20Gow%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66635b89a2a35d0ca376f093%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20tried%20attending%20a%20swinger's%20club%2C%20but%20Wilson%20says%20the%20other%20participants%20%26quot%3Blacked%20hygiene.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ESimone%20Lueck%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20films%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20middle-age%20sexual%20awakening.%20Wilson%20says%20she%20doesn't%20feel%20any%20jealousy%20when%20Gow%20is%20performing%20with%20porn%20stars.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20to%20watch%20him%20fuck%20other%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Gow%20feels%20the%20same%20way%20about%20seeing%20Wilson%20have%20sex%20with%20%26quot%3Bthese%20major%20stud-y%20guys%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BTo%20watch%20her%20turn%20them%20on%2C%20I'm%20just%20like%2C%20'Oh%20man%2C%20this%20is%20amazing.'%26quot%3B%20In%202016%2C%20Wilson%20became%20an%20administrator%20at%20Dickinson%20State%20University%20in%20western%20North%20Dakota.%20On%20days%20she%20was%20700%20miles%20away%2C%20Gow%20would%20often%20masturbate%20to%20their%20videos.%20%26quot%3BIt%20gets%20you%20through%20the%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shoots%20also%20brought%20out%20their%20creativity.%20Inspired%20by%20their%20love%20of%20food%2C%20they%20began%20shooting%20vegan%20cooking%20videos%20with%20porn%20stars%20and%20editing%20them%20together%20with%20their%20sex%20scenes%20%E2%80%94%20think%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffood-network-star-katie-lee-biegel-fridge-tour-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFood%20Network%3C%2Fa%3E%20meets%20Pornhub.%20In%20one%2C%20Gow%2C%20in%20a%20gray-checked%20button-down%2C%20and%20Wilson%2C%20in%20a%20purple%20top%2C%20face%20the%20camera%20behind%20a%20kitchen%20counter%20and%20explain%20how%20they're%20going%20to%20cook%20sweet-and-smoky%20soy-curl%20pizza.%20Then%20the%20adult%20star%20Lauren%20Phillips%2C%20the%20XBIZ%202024%20MILF%20performer%20of%20the%20year%2C%20bounds%20into%20the%20kitchen%2C%20breasts%20bouncing%20gloriously%20in%20a%20cropped%20tank%20top.%20As%20Phillips%20kneads%20soy%20curls%20in%20a%20marinade%20of%20tamari%2C%20maple%20syrup%2C%20and%20liquid%20smoke%2C%20Wilson%20smiles%20mischievously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20hands-on%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20Phillips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20Phillips%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWait%20till%20you've%20seen%20the%20scene%20we've%20shot%20with%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Gow%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20couple%20spent%20some%20%2480%2C000%20to%20shoot%2018%20porn%20films.%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20will%20go%20off%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20play%20golf%2C%26quot%3B%20Gow%20says.%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20go%20off%20and%20do%20this%20video.%26quot%3B%20His%20porn%20hobby%2C%20he%20says%2C%20usually%20didn't%20interfere%20with%20his%20work%20as%20chancellor.%20There%20was%20one%20day%20in%202015%2C%20though%2C%20when%20the%20university%20was%20trying%20to%20finalize%20plans%20for%20a%20visit%20from%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarack-obama-michelle-obama-net-worth-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBarack%20Obama%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Gow%20was%20on%20set%20in%20Arizona%20when%20he%20received%20a%20call%20from%20a%20staff%20member.%20He%20declined%20it%2C%20thinking%20it%20would%20interfere%20with%20his%20on-screen%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20they%20kept%20their%20porn%20films%20secret%2C%20Gow%20and%20Wilson%20self-published%20two%20books%20about%20their%20exploits%3A%20%26quot%3BMonogamy%20with%20Benefits%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BMarried%20with%20Benefits%3A%20Our%20Real-Life%20Adult-Industry%20Adventures.%26quot%3B%20They%20were%20careful%20to%20use%20pseudonyms%2C%20Geri%20and%20Jay%20Hart%2C%20identifying%20themselves%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-google-microsoft-ai-future-data-centers-monopoly-tech-industry-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20author%20bio%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20married%20woman%20and%20man%20who%20serve%20in%20executive%20positions%20at%20two%20well-known%20organizations%20in%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%20But%20next%20to%20the%20bio%2C%20seemingly%20oblivious%20to%20the%20ways%20of%20the%20internet%2C%20they%20included%20a%20photo%20of%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20their%20dining-room%20table%2C%20I%20sit%20next%20to%20Gow%20and%20Wilson%20as%20%26quot%3BJuicy%20Anniversary%26quot%3B%20starts%20to%20play.%20The%20video%20begins%20with%20Wilson%20in%20a%20slinky%20pink%20floral%20dress%20and%20silver%20heels%20and%20Gow%20in%20a%20beige%20sport%20coat%20and%20a%20white%20button-down.%20He%20presents%20her%20with%20several%20anniversary%20gifts%2C%20including%20a%20bracelet%20and%20a%20purple%20rabbit%20vibrator.%20The%20exchange%20goes%20on%20for%20six%20minutes.%20If%20you%20didn't%20know%20what%20was%20to%20come%2C%20you%20could%20be%20forgiven%20for%20mistaking%20it%20for%20a%20Lifetime%20rom-com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20clothes%20come%20off.%20Gow%2C%20in%20boxers%2C%20stands%20behind%20Wilson%2C%20caressing%20her%20breasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20table%2C%20Gow%20turns%20to%20me.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20me%20at%20this%20point%2C%20I'm%20like%2C%20OK%2C%20am%20I%20going%20to%20get%20hard%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20He'd%20taken%20Viagra%20for%20the%20shoot%2C%20but%20he%20remained%20worried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20background%2C%20Video%20Gow%20is%20moaning%20%26quot%3BOh%20yeah%26quot%3B%20as%20IRL%20Gow%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI've%20always%20had%20some%20ED%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn-screen%2C%20Gow%20begins%20to%20perform%20a%20variety%20of%20sexual%20acts%20on%20Wilson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20how%20well%20lit%20that%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Gow%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIRL%20Wilson%20nods%20in%20agreement.%20Video%20Wilson%20moans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe's%20multi-orgasmic%2C%26quot%3B%20Gow%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20always%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20adds.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20work%20at%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20close-up%20on%20Video%20Gow's%20lower%20torso%20as%20he%20thrusts.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20core%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20have%20a%20flat%20stomach.%26quot%3B%20Then%20he%20starts%20doing%20a%20play-by-play%2C%20like%20he's%20announcing%20a%20football%20game.%20%26quot%3BShe%20has%20two%20so%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20counting%20off%20her%20orgasms%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20here%20comes%20three.%26quot%3B%20As%20the%20video%20ends%20with%20the%20big%20finale%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20money%20shot%2C%20as%20it's%20known%20in%20the%20industry%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Video%20Gow%20stands%20above%20kneeling%20Video%20Wilson%2C%20arms%20outstretched.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20Christlike%2C%26quot%3B%20IRL%20Gow%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20kept%20their%20porn%20hobby%20hidden%2C%20it%20did%20bleed%20into%20their%20university%20life.%20In%202018%2C%20Gow%20and%20Wilson%20were%20filming%20a%20video%20with%20Nina%20Hartley%20when%20she%20mentioned%20she'd%20been%20paid%20to%20speak%20at%20schools%20like%20Dartmouth.%20Gow%20decided%20to%20bring%20her%20to%20UW-La%20Crosse%20for%20a%20talk%20called%20%26quot%3BFantasy%20vs.%20Reality%3A%20Viewing%20Adult%20Media%20with%20a%20Critical%20Eye.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Courtesy%20of%20Joe%20Gow%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666b2551ed9a404d829d82df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22794%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGow%20and%20Wilson%20during%20President%20Barack%20Obama's%202015%20visit%20to%20UW-La%20Crosse.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Joe%20Gow%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20backlash%20began%20the%20moment%20the%20event%20was%20announced.%20The%20chair%20of%20the%20faculty%20senate%20emailed%20Gow%20about%20his%20ire%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20controversial%20speaker%26quot%3B%20was%20being%20presented%20as%20the%20sole%20voice%20%26quot%3Bof%20a%20potentially%20triggering%20subject.%26quot%3B%20A%20student%20wrote%20that%20Hartley's%20visit%20%26quot%3Bencourages%20behavior%20that%20promotes%20sexual%20assault.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGow%2C%20who%20considers%20himself%20a%20champion%20of%20sex%20positivity%2C%20was%20undeterred.%20On%20the%20night%20of%20the%20event%2C%20he%20stood%20onstage%20in%20a%20suit%20and%20striped%20tie.%20%26quot%3BSexuality%2C%20pornography%3A%20These%20are%20things%20that%20I%20think%20we%20need%20to%20talk%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20have%20a%20speaker%20here%20with%20us%20to%20do%20that%20who%20is%20uniquely%20qualified%20on%20these%20subjects.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHartley%2C%20then%2059%2C%20blond%20hair%20cascading%20over%20her%20form-fitting%20black%20dress%2C%20began%20by%20leading%20the%20lecture%20hall%20in%20a%20chant.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20right%20to%20experience%20sexual%20pleasure%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20audience%20intoned.%20Then%20she%20discussed%20safe%20sex%2C%20her%20experiences%20on%20set%2C%20and%20the%20fantasies%20depicted%20in%20porn.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20nothing%20salacious%20about%20it%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Gow%20says.%20(Hartley%20declined%20to%20be%20interviewed.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20Hartley's%20talk%20was%20front-page%20news%20in%20the%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3ELa%20Crosse%20Tribune.%20When%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgentle-parenting-bust-millennial-parents-helicopter-kids-misbehave-permissive-authoritative-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparents%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20others%20complained%2C%20Gow%20defended%20himself%20in%20an%20op-ed%20article%2C%20arguing%20that%20he%20was%20helping%20promote%20the%20university's%20policy%20of%20academic%20freedom.%20The%20university%20disagreed.%20%26quot%3BYour%20defense%20of%20your%20actions%20is%20just%20making%20things%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20Gow's%20boss%2C%20the%20UW%20president%20Raymond%20Cross%2C%20told%20him.%20Cross%20officially%20reprimanded%20Gow%2C%20ordered%20an%20audit%20of%20his%20discretionary%20funds%2C%20and%20denied%20him%20a%20pending%20raise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGow%20issued%20a%20public%20apology%20and%20announced%20he%20would%20pay%20Hartley's%20%245%2C000%20speaking%20fee%20out%20of%20his%20own%20pocket.%20But%20the%20message%20from%20his%20superiors%20was%20clear%3A%20Even%20having%20so%20much%20as%20verbal%20intercourse%20with%20a%20porn%20star%20was%20off-limits%20for%20a%20university%20chancellor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20blowup%20took%20place%20last%20fall%2C%20after%20Gow%20announced%20at%20his%20annual%20start-of-the-school-year%20speech%20that%20he%20intended%20to%20retire%20as%20chancellor%20in%20May.%20He%20received%20a%20standing%20ovation.%20As%20Wilson%20stood%20beside%20him%20onstage%2C%20he%20mentioned%20that%20she%20was%20leaving%20academia%20and%20that%20the%20two%20of%20them%20were%20working%20on%20a%20YouTube%20cooking%20show.%20He%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20would%20remain%20on%20the%20faculty%20as%20a%20tenured%20professor%20in%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20accolades%20were%20universal.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Chancellor%20Gow%20steps%20down%20next%20year%2C%20he%20will%20be%20leaving%20UW-La%20Crosse%20much%20better%20off%20than%20it%20was%20when%20he%20arrived%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20university%20system's%20new%20president%20said.%20A%20public-radio%20story%20listing%20Gow's%20many%20achievements%20briefly%20mentioned%20the%20Hartley%20dustup.%20Gow%20spun%20the%20controversy%20as%20%26quot%3Bvery%20helpful%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20it%20had%20sparked%20global%20media%20attention%20for%20the%20university%20and%20elevated%20its%20commitment%20to%20free%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20their%20exit%20was%20pending%2C%20Gow%20and%20Wilson%20didn't%20waste%20any%20time%20in%20launching%20their%20porn%20career.%20That%20October%2C%20while%20he%20was%20still%20chancellor%2C%20they%20uploaded%20%26quot%3BJuicy%20Anniversary%26quot%3B%20and%20several%20other%20videos%20on%20LoyalFans%20and%20OnlyFans%20under%20the%20name%20SexyHappy%20Couple.%20The%20videos%20were%20paywalled.%20Only%20a%20handful%20of%20people%20watched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20Gow%20and%20Wilson%20were%20having%20dinner%20with%20their%20video%20editor.%20He%20suggested%20they%20might%20find%20a%20larger%20audience%20if%20they%20uploaded%20the%20videos%20on%20xHamster%20and%20Pornhub%2C%20where%20they%20could%20be%20watched%20for%20free.%20So%20the%20couple%20gave%20it%20a%20try%2C%20hoping%20they%20might%20get%20a%20few%20dozen%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20hundred%20people%20watched%20the%20first%20day.%20Within%20a%20week%2C%2010%2C000%20people%20were%20watching%20a%20day.%20Within%20two%20weeks%2C%20the%20views%20surpassed%201%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221173%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20still%20from%20%26quot%3BSexy%20Happy%20Couple%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20the%20couple%20shot%20on%20professional%20set%20in%20a%20penthouse%20loft%20in%20downtown%20LA.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666b2443764df161125997fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222311%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStills%20from%20Gow%20and%20Wilson's%20professionally%20shot%20films%20%26quot%3BSexy%20Happy%20Couple%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSweet%20Treat%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BSexy%20Healthy%20Cooking.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Joe%20Gow%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20were%20shocked.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20like%2C%20holy%20fuck%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20says.%20%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20know%3A%20Does%20anybody%20want%20to%20see%20a%20couple%20in%20their%2050s%20having%20sex%3F%20And%20the%20amazing%20thing%20was%2C%20yes%2C%20they%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20Gow%20realized%20they%20might%20have%20jumped%20the%20gun%20by%20posting%20their%20porn%20videos%20for%20free.%20%26quot%3BSooner%20or%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20worried%2C%20%26quot%3Bsomebody%20we%20know%20is%20going%20to%20see%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20sooner.%20On%20December%2019%2C%20three%20weeks%20after%20the%20videos%20were%20posted%2C%20Gow%20received%20a%20call%20from%20the%20university's%20legal%20team%20saying%20they%20needed%20to%20discuss%20a%20%26quot%3Bpersonnel%20matter%26quot%3B%20with%20him.%20He%20didn't%20think%20much%20of%20it.%20As%20chancellor%2C%20he%20regularly%20talked%20to%20the%20school's%20lawyers.%20But%20when%20the%20meeting%20began%20over%20Zoom%20the%20following%20day%2C%20he%20realized%20it%20was%20about%20him.%20Someone%20had%20seen%20the%20videos%20and%20forwarded%20them%20to%20the%20president's%20chief%20of%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20call%2C%20the%20deputy%20general%20counsel%20and%20the%20deputy%20HR%20director%20questioned%20Gow%20about%20the%20videos%20and%20his%20books%2C%20which%20they%20had%20also%20discovered.%20He%20admitted%20everything%20and%20cleared%20up%20a%20misconception.%20The%20lawyers%20thought%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Btheir%20big%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20Gow%20says%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20couple%20had%20been%20paid%20by%20the%20porn%20studios%2C%20when%20in%20fact%20it%20was%20the%20other%20way%20around.%20Gow%20explained%20that%20he%20had%20never%20made%20more%20than%20%241%2C000%20from%20his%20%26quot%3Bexpensive%20hobby%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20why%20he%20never%20reported%20it%20on%20the%20financial%20statement%20he%20was%20required%20to%20file%20each%20year%20with%20the%20state.%20%26quot%3BThat%20seemed%20to%20satisfy%20my%20system%20colleagues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20later%20wrote%20in%20the%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EChronicle%20of%20Higher%20Education%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20they%20ended%20the%20meeting%20cordially%2C%20giving%20me%20no%20indication%20of%20what%20might%20happen%20next.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20days%20later%2C%20as%20Gow%20and%20Wilson%20were%20flying%20back%20to%20La%20Crosse%20after%20visiting%20his%2093-year-old%20mother%20for%20Christmas%2C%20Gow%20learned%20he%20had%20been%20fired%20as%20chancellor.%20The%20termination%20letter%20said%20he%20had%20failed%20to%20properly%20report%20his%20income%20from%20the%20porn%20videos%20and%20had%20violated%20%26quot%3Bprohibitions%20for%20using%20one's%20public%20position%20for%20private%20benefit.%26quot%3B%20The%20president%20of%20the%20university%20system%20released%20a%20statement%20calling%20Gow's%20actions%20%26quot%3Babhorrent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGow%20was%20placed%20on%20paid%20administrative%20leave%20for%20the%20spring%20semester%2C%20but%20he%20retained%20his%20status%20as%20a%20faculty%20member.%20Firing%20a%20tenured%20professor%20is%20extremely%20hard%2C%20for%20good%20reason.%20The%20whole%20point%20of%20tenure%20is%20to%20let%20faculty%20express%20themselves%20freely%2C%20without%20fear%20of%20reprisal.%20Termination%20requires%20just%20cause.%20Sexual%20assault%2C%20domestic%20violence%2C%20and%20sexual%20harassment%20all%20count.%20Consensual%20sexual%20activity%20doesn't.%20The%20only%20mention%20of%20porn%20in%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin's%20bylaws%20is%20a%20rule%20against%20watching%20it%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20a%20review%20of%20Gow's%20tenure%2C%20the%20university%20hired%20a%20white-shoe%20law%20firm%20and%20a%20forensic%20analyst%20from%20the%20publicly%20traded%20firm%20FTI%20Consulting%20to%20investigate%20his%20actions.%20His%20university-issued%20computer%20was%20seized%2C%20along%20with%20Wilson's.%20Then%20the%20most%20accomplished%20chancellor%20in%20the%20school's%20history%20was%20barred%20from%20campus%2C%20unless%20accompanied%20by%20a%20police%20escort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20morning%20after%20I%20watch%20%26quot%3BJuicy%20Anniversary%26quot%3B%20at%20their%20dining%20table%2C%20Gow%20takes%20me%20to%20Planet%20Fitness.%20He%20wants%20to%20show%20me%20his%20workout%20routine.%20As%20Gow%20does%20mountain%20climbers%2C%20his%20skinny%20legs%20pumping%2C%20his%20longtime%20trainer%2C%20Tony%20Tomich%2C%20offers%20a%20full-throated%20defense%20of%20his%20client.%20Gow%20and%20Wilson's%20porn%20%26quot%3Bwasn't%20hurting%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Tomich%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20sad%20in%20this%20day%20and%20age%2C%20in%20a%20university%20environment%2C%20where%20you're%20supposed%20to%20be%20open%20minded.%20This%20isn't%20Communist%20China.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20on%20campus%20echo%20those%20concerns.%20After%20Gow's%20workout%2C%20I%20head%20to%20the%20student%20center%20to%20meet%20Easton%20Moberg%2C%20a%20sophomore%20who%20has%20covered%20the%20Gow%20scandal%20as%20managing%20editor%20of%20the%20student%20newspaper%2C%20The%20Racquet%20Press.%20The%20first%20thing%20I%20notice%20in%20his%20office%20is%20a%20brochure%20from%20the%20women's%20and%20gender%20studies%20department%20pinned%20to%20a%20wall%3A%20%26quot%3BYour%20Comprehensive%20Guide%20to%20Clitoral%20Masturbation%20and%20Other%20Pleasures.%26quot%3B%20A%20recent%20issue%20of%20the%20paper%20featured%20a%20satirical%20story%20with%20a%20photo%20of%20Gow%2C%20Wilson%2C%20and%20Nina%20Hartley%20under%20the%20headline%20%26quot%3BGow%20to%20Teach%20Culinary%20Class.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoberg%20tells%20me%20he%20used%20to%20have%20a%20flag%20with%20Gow's%20face%20on%20it%20pinned%20inside%20the%20house%20he%20shared%20with%20fellow%20students.%20Gow%20%26quot%3Bwas%20just%20well%20respected%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BStudents%20loved%20him.%26quot%3B%20After%20the%20porn%20became%20public%2C%20he%20and%20his%20friends%20found%20the%20situation%20%26quot%3Bhilarious.%26quot%3B%20His%20roommate%20began%20%26quot%3Bcranking%20out%20memes%20instantly.%26quot%3B%20Still%2C%20Moberg%20doesn't%20think%20Gow%20should%20be%20stripped%20of%20tenure.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20pro-First%20Amendment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20the%20right%20to%20speak%20freely%20and%20write%20freely.%20He%20should%20be%20able%20to%20do%20whatever%20he%20wants%20to%20do%20freely%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20and%20woman%20holding%20hands.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66635b04ed9a404d829bd520%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221969%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20Gow%20and%20Wilson%20had%20managed%20to%20keep%20their%20porn%20careers%20secret%20for%20a%20few%20more%20months%2C%20their%20videos%20wouldn't%20be%20generating%20nearly%20as%20much%20revenue.%3Cp%3ESimone%20Lueck%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20a%20janitor%20in%20the%20student%20center%20tells%20me%20he%20feels%20the%20same%20way%20about%20Gow's%20indiscretions.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20what%20he%20did%20was%20right%2C%20but%20that%20was%20his%20own%20private%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20like%20what%20someone's%20doing%2C%20just%20go%20to%20another%20website%2C%20just%20keep%20your%20mouth%20shut.%20You%20don't%20need%20to%20set%20someone%20up%20and%20take%20them%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20gestures%20to%20an%20empty%20wall%20that%20used%20to%20contain%20portraits%20of%20past%20chancellors.%20%26quot%3BGow%20was%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20pointing%20to%20a%20blank%20spot%20that%20has%20been%20repainted%20eggshell%20white.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20university%20completed%20its%20investigation%20and%20provided%20Gow%20with%20a%20copy%20of%20its%20report%2C%20which%20stretches%20to%20318%20pages.%20After%20watching%20over%2011%20hours%20of%20the%20couple's%20porn%2C%20the%20investigators%20demurely%20concluded%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bdialog%20and%20video%20content%20would%20likely%20be%20considered%20offensive%20to%20many%20but%20were%20not%20likely%20illegal.%26quot%3B%20Nonetheless%2C%20the%20report%20brims%20with%20salacious%20details%2C%20couched%20in%20a%20kind%20of%20tortured%20bureaucratic%20prudery%20unseen%20since%20the%20Starr%20Report.%20Breasts%20are%20%26quot%3Btorsos%26quot%3B%3B%20scenes%20end%20with%20various%20things%20being%20%26quot%3Bconsumed.%26quot%3B%20Twenty-five%20pages%20are%20devoted%20to%20sex-toy%20marketing%20emails%20that%20were%20sent%20to%20Gow's%20and%20Wilson's%20university%20email%20addresses.%20The%20emails%20featured%20images%20of%20vibrators%2C%20pocket%20pussies%2C%20and%20vibrating%20asses.%20Gow%20says%20he%20never%20visited%20porn%20sites%20while%20at%20work.%20The%20university's%20president%2C%20general%20counsel%2C%20and%20interim%20chancellor%20all%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20offered%20to%20settle%20the%20case%20without%20issuing%20charges%20if%20Gow%20would%20agree%20to%20retire%20from%20the%20faculty.%20When%20he%20refused%2C%20he%20was%20charged%20with%2021%20violations%20of%20university%20policy%2C%20including%20refusing%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20investigation%2C%20receiving%20emails%20containing%20pornographic%20images%20on%20university%20computers%2C%20engaging%20in%20%26quot%3Bunethical%20and%20potentially%20illegal%20conduct%26quot%3B%20by%20paying%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20female%20escorts%20and%20strippers%20and%20paying%20for%20Wilson%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20a%20male%20escort%2C%20and%20damaging%20the%20university's%20reputation%20by%20making%20porn%20and%20posting%20it%20online.%20The%20university%20also%20complained%2C%20somewhat%20penuriously%2C%20that%20Gow%20%26quot%3Btook%20a%20large%20volume%20of%20leftover%20catered%20wine%20from%20the%20Chancellor's%20Box%26quot%3B%20after%20two%20football%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGow%20decided%20to%20fight%20his%20dismissal%20on%20First%20Amendment%20grounds.%20On%20April%2017%2C%20he%20formally%20requested%20a%20public%20hearing%20to%20review%20his%20termination%20as%20a%20tenured%20faculty%20member.%20Under%20the%20university's%20rules%2C%20a%20faculty%20member%20will%20chair%20the%20tribunal%2C%20which%20is%20scheduled%20to%20convene%20on%20June%2019%2C%20and%20each%20side%20will%20have%20three%20hours%20to%20present%20its%20case.%20It%20will%20be%20the%20state's%20first%20hearing%20over%20a%20faculty%20member's%20tenure%20in%2023%20years%2C%20and%20the%20first%20ever%20over%20porn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20the%20trial%20of%20Socrates%2C%26quot%3B%20Gow%20says%20with%20characteristic%20modesty.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20about%20corrupting%20the%20morals%20of%20youth.%20They%20wanted%20me%20to%20drink%20the%20hemlock.%26quot%3B%20He%20plans%20to%20defend%20himself%20at%20the%20hearing%2C%20as%20Socrates%20did%2C%20and%20he%20believes%20the%20tribunal%20will%20ultimately%20see%20that%2C%20as%20he%20recently%20told%20a%20local%20La%20Crosse%20news%20station%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20a%20couple%20does%20on%20their%20vacation%2C%20on%20their%20own%20time%20with%20their%20own%20money%20and%20on%20social%20media%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat's%20their%20own%20business%2C%20and%20that%20shouldn't%20disqualify%20one%20from%20being%20a%20faculty%20member.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGow%20may%20be%20right.%20But%20it's%20a%20tough%20sell%20at%20a%20moment%20when%20leading%20universities%20across%20the%20country%20are%20under%20attack%20by%20the%20far%20right.%20Experts%20are%20skeptical%20that%20Gow%20will%20prevail%20on%20free-speech%20grounds.%20%26quot%3BBeing%20in%20a%20pornographic%20movie%20is%20generally%20not%20viewed%20as%20speech%20on%20matters%20of%20public%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Eugene%20Volokh%2C%20a%20First%20Amendment%20scholar%20at%20Stanford.%20He%20points%20to%20the%20precedent%20set%20by%20City%20of%20San%20Diego%20v.%20Roe%2C%20where%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20determined%20that%20a%20police%20officer%20could%20be%20fired%20for%20selling%20videos%20of%20himself%20masturbating%20on%20eBay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20hearing%2C%20Gow%20and%20Wilson%20have%20already%20paid%20a%20steep%20price%20for%20their%20perceived%20transgressions.%20Wilson's%2037-year-old%20daughter%20didn't%20speak%20to%20her%20for%20five%20months%20and%20has%20cut%20her%20off%20from%20contact%20with%20her%20two%20young%20grandchildren.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20hurt%20you%20as%20much%20as%20you%20hurt%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20daughter%20told%20her.%20Gow's%20mother%20called%20him%20%26quot%3Bdisgusting.%26quot%3B%20Wilson's%2082-year-old%20mother%2C%20Diane%2C%20wouldn't%20speak%20to%20her%20daughter%20for%20a%20month.%20When%20she%20finally%20relented%2C%20she%20wrapped%20Wilson%20in%20a%20hug%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYour%20reputation%20is%20ruined.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20leave%20La%20Crosse%2C%20I%20pay%20one%20last%20visit%20to%20Gow%20and%20Wilson's%20home%2C%20where%20they%20and%20Diane%20are%20having%20their%20Sunday-night%20ritual%20of%20wine%20and%20snacks.%20%26quot%3BI%20decided%20I%20wasn't%20going%20to%20lose%20my%20relationship%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Diane%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20them%2C%20I'm%20not%20condoning%20what%20you've%20done.%20But%20I%20will%20accept%20it.%26quot%3B%20What%20upsets%20her%20most%20is%20that%20her%20daughter%20and%20granddaughter%20aren't%20speaking%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20have%20a%20relationship%20with%20her%2C%20but%20she%20won't%20talk%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20has%20that%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Diane%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20have%20a%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20says.%20They%20both%20begin%20to%20cry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20worst%20part%20of%20the%20whole%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Gow%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20love%20those%20kids%20too.%20To%20just%20be%20shut%20out%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0his%20voice%20breaks%2C%20and%20he%20joins%20the%20weeping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Diane%20is%20on%20her%20second%20glass%20of%20red%2C%20she%20tells%20me%20about%20how%20she%20remained%20a%20virgin%20in%20college.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20zero%20sex%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20lived%20on%20a%20farm%2C%20and%20that's%20how%20I%20learned%2C%20watching%20the%20animals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20phone%20rings%20%E2%80%94%20her%20granddaughter%2C%20Wilson's%20daughter%2C%20is%20FaceTiming%20her.%20Diane%20walks%20into%20the%20living%20room%20to%20take%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ask%20Gow%20and%20Wilson%20if%20I%20can%20see%20their%20OnlyFans.%20Gow%20logs%20in%2C%20showing%20me%20a%20chart%20of%20their%20subscribers.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%20what%20that%20bump%20is%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20day%20they%20fired%20me%20and%20it%20got%20into%20the%20media.%20We%20went%20from%2024%20subscribers%20to%209%2C666%20literally%20overnight.%26quot%3B%20In%20two%20months%2C%20they%20made%20%2460%2C000%20from%20the%20platform.%20They've%20also%20signed%20with%20Sssh.com%2C%20a%20porn%20studio%20for%20women%20and%20couples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joe%20Gow%20and%20wife.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66635bd2e079049018171ef2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20a%20couple%20does%20on%20their%20vacation%2C%20on%20their%20own%20time%20with%20their%20own%20money%20and%20on%20social%20media%2C%20that's%20their%20own%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Gow.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20shouldn't%20disqualify%20one%20from%20being%20a%20faculty%20member.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ESimone%20Lueck%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20get%20into%20this%20for%20the%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Gow%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20when%20my%20job%20is%20under%20threat%20and%20our%20health%20insurance%20is%20under%20threat%2C%20it's%20good%20to%20be%20able%20to%20make%2C%20like%2C%20%24300%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20therein%20lies%20the%20rub%2C%20as%20it%20were.%20If%20Gow%20and%20Wilson%20had%20managed%20to%20keep%20their%20porn%20careers%20secret%20for%20a%20few%20more%20months%2C%20their%20videos%20wouldn't%20be%20generating%20nearly%20as%20much%20revenue%20as%20they%20are%20now.%20Gow%20could%20have%20stepped%20down%20to%20widespread%20acclaim%20before%20going%20on%20to%20a%20second%20act%20that%20combined%20recipes%20for%20vegan%20country-style%20ribs%20with%20scenes%20of%20graphic%