hat%20they%20have%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20whether%20Canada%20will%20invite%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20the%20G7%20Summit%20in%202025%2C%20Trudeau%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20appreciate%20the%20keenness%20with%20it%20with%20which%20Canadians%20are%20looking%20forward%20to%20next%20year's%20G7.%20However%2C%20Italy%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20President%20of%20this%20G7%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20this%20year%20and%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20working%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Meloni%20and%20all%20my%20G7%20Partners%20on%20the%20broad%20range%20of%20issues%20that%20we've%20talked%20about.%20I%20will%20have%20more%20to%20say%20about%20next%20year's%20G7%20when%20we%20assume%20the%20G7%20Presidency%20next%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20G7%20summit%20was%20held%20in%20Italy's%20Apulia%20region%20from%20June%2013-15%2C%20where%20India%20was%20invited%20as%20an%20'Outreach%20Country'%20and%20had%20participation%20from%20the%20seven%20member%20countries%2C%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Canada%2C%20Germany%2C%20Italy%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20France%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20G7%20Leaders'%20Summit%20will%20be%20hosted%20in%20Kananaskis%2C%20Alberta%20province%20of%20Canada%20in%202025.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Canadian%20PM%20Justin%20Trudeau%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BJust%20announced%3A%20The%20next%20%40G7%20Leaders'%20Summit%20will%20be%20hosted%20here%20in%20Canada%20--%20in%20Kananaskis%2C%20Alberta%20--%20in%202025.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau's%20statement%20came%20after%20he%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G7%20Summit%20in%20Italy's%20Apulia%20on%20Friday.%20The%20meeting%20between%20the%20two%20leaders%20was%20the%20first%20amid%20strained%20diplomatic%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BMet%20Canadian%20PM%20%40JustinTrudeau%20at%20the%20G7%20Summit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20were%20strained%20after%20Trudeau%20accused%20the%20%26quot%3Bagents%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%26quot%3B%20of%20killing%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20Canada%20last%20year.%20However%2C%20India%20has%20dismissed%20the%20accusations%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENijjar%2C%20who%20was%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20by%20India's%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20in%202020%2C%20was%20shot%20and%20killed%20outside%20a%20Gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%20in%20June%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20said%20that%20Canada%20has%20not%20provided%20any%20%26quot%3Bspecific%26quot%3B%20evidence%20or%20relevant%20information%20in%20the%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20killing%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20May%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20denied%20receiving%20any%20evidence%20implicating%20Indian%20nationals'%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20in%20Canada%20of%20India-designated%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20media%20queries%20here%2C%20Jaishankar%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20read%20that%20another%20arrest%20has%20been%20made.%20If%20that%20person%20is%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20then%20usually%20by%20consular%20practice%2C%20you%20inform%20the%20government%20or%20the%20embassy%20of%20the%20country%20of%20origin.%20But%20beyond%20that%2C%20we%20have%20long%20maintained%20that%20if%20anything%2C%20any%20event%20in%20Canada%2C%20any%20violence%20in%20Canada%2C%20has%20any%20evidence%20or%20information%20which%20is%20relevant%20to%20be%20investigated%20in%20India%2C%20we%20are%20open%20to%20investigating%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasised%20that%20while%20any%20Indian%20national's%20arrest%20would%20usually%20prompt%20notification%20to%20the%20government%20or%20embassy%2C%20no%20specific%20evidence%20justifying%20investigation%20by%20Indian%20agencies%20has%20been%20received%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20to%20date%2C%20we%20have%20never%20received%20anything%20which%20is%20specific%20and%20worthy%20of%20being%20pursued%20by%20our%20investigative%20agencies.%20And%20I'm%20not%20aware%20anything%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20in%20that%20regard%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said%20at%20a%20media%20interaction%20at%20a%20seminar%20on%20Indian%20Capital%20Markets%20'Roadmap%20for%20Viksit%20Bharat'%20at%20the%20National%20Stock%20Exchange%20(NSE)%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20after%20the%20Canadian%20Police%20arrested%20a%20fourth%20suspect%20over%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar.%20The%20accused%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Amandeep%20Singh%20(22)%2C%20Canada-based%20CBC%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Integrated%20Homicide%20Investigation%20Team%20(IHIT)%20in%20British%20Columbia%2C%20Singh%20was%20already%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20Peel%20Regional%20Police%20in%20Ontario%20for%20unrelated%20firearms%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20that%20Singh%20is%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20splitting%20his%20time%20in%20Canada%20in%20Brampton%2C%20Ontario%3B%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20and%20Abbotsford%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20CBC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20have%20not%20shared%20any%20further%20details%20of%20the%20arrest%2C%20citing%20ongoing%20investigations%20and%20court%20processes.%20The%20development%20came%20days%20after%20the%20Canadian%20police%20arrested%20three%20Indian%20nationals%20--%20Karan%20Brar%2C%20Kamalpreet%20Singh%20and%20Karanpreet%20Singh%20--%20in%20Edmonton.%20The%20trio%20was%20charged%20with%20first-degree%20murder%20and%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20murder%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20homicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C