20become%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20Indian%20team.%20He%20will%20replace%20the%20outgoing%20Rahul%20Dravid%20after%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BCCI%20source%20privy%20of%20the%20developments%20told%20Dainik%20Bhaskar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20added%20that%20Gambhir%20told%20the%20BCCI%20that%20he%20would%20accept%20the%20job%20if%20he%20gets%20to%20decide%20the%20support%20staff.%20His%20demand%20was%20accepted%20and%20the%20board%20will%20make%20an%20official%20announcement%20on%20Gambhir's%20appointment%20as%20head%20coach%20later%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravi%20Shastri%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41719-ravishankar-jayadritha-shastri-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavi%20Shastri%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20head%20coach%2C%20Vikram%20Rathour%20had%20replaced%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sanjay%20Bangar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F117-sanjay-bangar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Bangar%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20batting%20coach.%20Rathour%20managed%20to%20keep%20his%20place%20in%20the%20support%20staff%20even%20after%20Dravid%20replaced%20Shastri%20as%20the%20head%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Paras%20Mhambrey%20and%20T%20Dilip%20are%20the%20bowling%20and%20fielding%20coach%2C%20respectively.%20The%20report%20also%20revealed%20that%20Gambhir%20will%20not%20only%20make%20changes%20to%20the%20support%20staff%2C%20but%20also%20in%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Gambhir's%20mentorship%2C%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20clinched%20the%20IPL%202024%20title.%20His%20leadership%20at%20KKR%20has%20been%20widely%20praised%2C%20contributing%20to%20his%20rising%20profile%20as%20a%20top%20coaching%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20recent%20event%2C%20Gambhir%20suggested%20that%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20bigger%20honour%20than%20coaching%20the%20national%20team%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26q