ETesla%20chief%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20have%20started%20a%20debate%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20on%20whether%20the%20world%20should%20switch%20to%20paper%20voting%20and%20discard%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20over%20possible%20risks%20of%20being%20hacked%20and%20manipulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20also%20joined%20in%2C%20backing%20Mr%20Musk's%20apprehension%20of%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk%20set%20the%20ball%20rolling%20with%20his%20post%20questioning%20EVMs'%20reliability%2C%20referring%20to%20media%20reports%20that%20Puerto%20Rico's%20elections%20saw%20voting%20irregularities%20in%20hundreds%20of%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLuckily%2C%20there%20was%20a%20paper%20trail%20so%20the%20problem%20was%20identified%20and%20vote%20tallies%20corrected%2C%26quot%3B%20independent%20US%20presidential%20candidate%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20who%20headed%20the%20electronics%20and%20information%20technology%20ministry%20in%20the%20previous%20government%2C%20in%20his%20reply%20to%20Mr%20Musk%20indicated%20the%20X%20owner's%20comment%20made%20it%20seem%20like%20%26quot%3Bno%20one%20can%20build%20secure%20digital%20hardware.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Union%20Minister%20said%20he'd%20be%20happy%20to%20run%20a%20tutorial%20for%20Mr%20Musk%20on%20how%20to%20build%20a%20secure%20EVM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20huge%20sweeping%20generalisation%20statement%20that%20implies%20no%20one%20can%20build%20secure%20digital%20hardware.%20Wrong.%20Elon%20Musk's%20view%20may%20apply%20to%20the%20US%20and%20other%20places%20-%20where%20they%20use%20regular%20compute%20platforms%20to%20build%20internet-connected%20voting%20machines%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20said%20in%20a%20reply%20to%20Mr%20Musk's%20post%20that%20EVMs%20weren't%20reliable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20a%20huge%20sweeping%20generalization%20statement%20that%20implies%20no%20one%20can%20build%20secure%20digital%20hardware.%20Wrong.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40elonmusk%3C%2Fa%3E%20's%20view%20may%20apply%20to%20US%20n%20other%20places%20-%20where%20they%20use%20regular%20compute%20platforms%20to%20build%20Internet%20connected%20Voting%20machines.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnBut%20Indian%20EVMs%20are%20custom...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGiaCqU1n7O%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGiaCqU1n7O%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40RajeevRC_X)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRajeevRC_X%2Fstatus%2F1802195948254466461%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20used%20EVMs%20in%20the%20recently%20held%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Many%20political%20leaders%2C%20mostly%20from%20the%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20had%20said%20the%20same%20thing%20as%20Mr%20Musk%20has%20said%2C%20i.e.%20EVMs%20need%20to%20be%20replaced%20with%20paper%20voting%2C%20for%20any%20doubt%20in%20voters'%20minds%20can%20wipe%20out%20trust%20from%20the%20entire%20democratic%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20Join%20EVM%20Debate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%2C%20too%2C%20has%20been%20a%20fierce%20critic%20of%20EVMs.%20%26quot%3BEVMs%20in%20India%20are%20a%20'black%20box%2C'%20and%20nobody%20is%20allowed%20to%20scrutinise%20them.%20Serious%20concerns%20are%20being%20raised%20about%20transparency%20in%20our%20electoral%20process.%20Democracy%20ends%20up%20becoming%20a%20sham%20and%20prone%20to%20fraud%20when%20institutions%20lack%20accountability%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20in%20response%20to%20Mr%20Musk's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EEVMs%20in%20India%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bblack%20box%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20nobody%20is%20allowed%20to%20scrutinize%20them.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSerious%20concerns%20are%20being%20raised%20about%20transparency%20in%20our%20electoral%20process.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDemocracy%20ends%20up%20becoming%20a%20sham%20and%20prone%20to%20fraud%20when%20institutions%20lack%20accountability.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fnysn5S8DCF%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fnysn5S8DCF%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7sdTWJXOAb%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F7sdTWJXOAb%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20(%40RahulGandhi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%2Fstatus%2F1802219727068037545%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20Opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20ally%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%2C%20said%20technology%20experts%20around%20the%20world%20are%20openly%20writing%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20EVM%20tampering.%20%26quot%3BWe%20reiterate%20our%20demand%20that%20all%20future%20elections%20be%20conducted%20using%20ballot%20papers%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Indian%20EVMs%2C%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20said%20they%20are%20custom%20designed%20and%20isolated%20from%20any%20kind%20of%20network%20or%20media.%20%26quot%3B...%20no%20connectivity%2C%20no%20Bluetooth%2C%20Wi-FI%2C%20internet%2C%20i.e.%20there%20is%20no%20way%20in.%20(There%20are)%20factory%20programmed%20controllers%20that%20cannot%20be%20reprogrammed.%20Electronic%20voting%20machines%20can%20be...%20built%20right%20as%20India%20has%20done...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BAnything%20can%20be%20hacked%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Union%20Minister%20agreed%20that%20%26quot%3Banything%20is%20possible%26quot%3B%2C%20at%20least%20in%20theory.%20%26quot%3B...%20With%20quantum%20compute%2C%20I%20can%20decrypt%20any%20level%20of%20encryption.%20With%20lab-level%20tech%20and%20plenty%20of%20resources%2C%20I%20can%20hack%20any%20digital%20hardware%2Fsystem%20including%20the%20flight%20controls%20of%20a%20glass%20cockpit%20of%20a%20jet%2C%20etc.%20But%20that's%20a%20different%20type%20of%20conversation%20from%20EVMs%20being%20secure%20and%20reliable...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20also%20ruled%20it%20can't%20dictate%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%2C%20a%20constitutional%20authority%2C%20on%20the%20matter%20of%20EVMs.%20The%20EC%20has%20long%20maintained%20India's%20EVMs%20are%20foolproof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20EVM%20has%20a%20control%20unit%20and%20a%20balloting%20unit.%20These%20are%20connected%20by%20a%20cable.%20These%20are%20also%20connected%20with%20a%20VVPAT%20--%20Voter%20Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20--%20machine.%20This%20machine%20enables%20a%20voter%20to%20see%20if%20the%20vote%20was%20cast%20properly%20and%20went%20to%20the%20candidate%20he%2Fshe%20supports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEuropean%20nations%20have%20reverted%20to%20the%20ballot%20voting%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718527680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F9uivlvpo_elon-musk-rajeev-chandrasekhar_625x300_16_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhack-yes-hack-no-elon-musk-vs-rajeev-chandrasekhar-on-evms-5901635%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20chief%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20have%20started%20a%20debate%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20on%20whether%20the%20world%20should%20switch%20to%20paper%20voting%20and%20discard%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhack-yes-hack-no-elon-musk-vs-rajeev-chandrasekhar-on-evms-5901635%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhack-yes-hack-no-elon-musk-vs-rajeev-chandrasekhar-on-evms-5901635%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhack-yes-hack-no-elon-musk-vs-rajeev-chandrasekhar-on-evms-5901635%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amit%20Shah%20Chairs%20Key%20Meet%20As%204%20J%26amp%3BK%20Terror%20Attacks%20In%20A%20Week%20Sets%20Off%20Alarm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20top%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20security%20establishment%20met%20for%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20this%20morning%20to%20review%20the%20security%20situation%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20where%20four%20terror%20attacks%20within%20in%20a%20week%20has%20set%20off%20alarm%20bells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%2C%20also%20attended%20by%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20and%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20and%20Home%20Secretary%20Ajay%20Bhalla%2C%20comes%20less%20than%20a%20fortnight%20before%20the%20Amarnath%20Yatra%2C%20known%20to%20draw%20lakhs%20of%20pilgrims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20security%20officers%20who%20attended%20the%20meeting%20include%20Director%20of%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20Tapan%20Deka%2C%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20General%20Manoj%20Pande%2C%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20(designate)%20Lt%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%20and%20CRPF%20Director%20General%20Anish%20Dayal%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Territory%20is%20on%20high%20alert%20after%20four%20terror%20strikes%20in%20the%20past%20week.%20Nine%20pilgrims%20were%20killed%20and%2041%20others%20injured%20when%20terrorists%20targeted%20a%20bus%20in%20Reasi%20on%20June%209.%20A%20CRPF%20personnel%20was%20killed%20and%20several%20others%20injured%20in%20the%20other%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20back-to-back%20attacks%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20challenge%20for%20the%20third%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20which%20has%20repeatedly%20showcased%20the%20relative%20calm%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20after%20its%20special%20status%20was%20revoked%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20beginning%20his%20third%20term%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20chaired%20a%20meeting%20with%20top%20officials%20to%20discuss%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attacks%20have%20also%20raised%20security%20concerns%20surrounding%20the%20Amarnath%20Yatra%2C%20which%20begins%20on%20June%2029%20and%20will%20continue%20till%20August%2019.%20Pilgrims%20to%20the%20cave%20shrine%20travel%20through%20two%20routes%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20--%20Baltal%20and%20Pahalgam.%20Last%20year%2C%20over%204%20lakh%20people%20visited%20the%20shrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20police%20have%20said%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20coordinated%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20pilgrims'%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718527440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F10qae2l_amit-shah-review-meet_625x300_16_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-reviews-jammu-and-kashmir-security-amarnath-yatra-prep-after-4-terror-attacks-5901541%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20top%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20security%20establishment%20met%20for%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20this%20morning%20to%20review%20the%20security%20situation%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20where%20four%20terror%20attacks%20within%20in%20a%20week%20has%20set%20off%20alarm%20bells.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-reviews-jammu-and-kashmir-security-amarnath-yatra-prep-after-4-terror-attacks-5901541%22%