a%20flight%20attendant%20and%20passengers%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%20the%20violent%20behaviour%20before%20she%20was%20sedated%20and%20removed%20from%20the%20plane%20once%20it%20landed%20at%20the%20Charlotte%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20is%20being%20charged%20fine%20up%20to%20%2445%2C000%20for%20assaulting%20and%20threatening%20crew%20members%20and%20posing%20%26quot%3Ban%20imminent%20threat%20to%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20aircraft%2C%20crew%20and%20passengers%2C%26quot%3B%20%2427%2C950%20for%20attempting%20to%20open%20the%20cabin%20door%20in-flight%20and%20%249%2C000%20for%20interfering%20with%20the%20crew%20member's%20duties%2C%20the%20USA%20Today%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718525340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fmr9ml9q_us-woman_625x300_16_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-who-kicked-spat-at-passengers-on-american-airlines-sued-over-unpaid-81-950-fine-5901362%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2034-year-old%20US%20woman%20has%20been%20sued%20for%20failing%20to%20pay%20%2481%2C950%20fine%20for%20assaulting%20co-passengers%20on%20an%20American%20Airlines%20flight%20in%202021%2C%20a%20report%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-who-kicked-spat-at-passengers-on-american-airlines-sued-over-unpaid-81-950-fine-5901362%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-who-kicked-spat-at-passengers-on-american-airlines-sued-over-unpaid-81-950-fine-5901362%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-who-kicked-spat-at-passengers-on-american-airlines-sued-over-unpaid-81-950-fine-5901362%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EVMs%20in%20India%20are%20'black%20box'%2C%20nobody%20allowed%20to%20scrutinise%20them%3A%20Rahul%22%