h.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPHzJsoXpLh%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPHzJsoXpLh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1801977467218853932%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2015%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spotlight%20on%20EVM%20security%20has%20intensified%20due%20to%20recent%20controversies%20in%20Puerto%20Rico.%20The%20primary%20elections%20there%20were%20plagued%20by%20numerous%20irregularities%20linked%20to%20EVMs.%20However%2C%20a%20paper%20trail%20allowed%20election%20officials%20to%20identify%20and%20correct%20vote%20tallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk's%20remark%20was%20in%20response%20to%2C%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%2C%20nephew%20of%20former%20US%20President%20John%20F%20Kennedy%20and%20an%20independent%20hopeful%20for%20the%202024%20US%20Elections%2C%20who%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BPuerto%20Rico's%20primary%20elections%20just%20experienced%20hundreds%20of%20voting%20irregularities%20related%20to%20electronic%20voting%20machines%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Associated%20Press.%20Luckily%2C%20there%20was%20a%20paper%20trail%20so%20the%20problem%20was%20identified%20and%20vote%20tallies%20corrected.%20What%20happens%20in%20jurisdictions%20where%20there%20is%20no%20paper%20trail%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKennedy%20Jr%20advocated%20for%20a%20return%20to%20paper%20ballots%20to%20prevent%20electronic%20interference%20in%20elections%2C%20ensuring%20that%20every%20vote%20is%20counted%20and%20elections%20remain%20secure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20concerns%20over%20EVMs%20are%20gaining%20traction%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20scenario%20in%20India%20presents%20a%20contrasting%20picture.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftop-experts-from-iit-who-helped-design-indias-most-tamper-proof-evms-5728218%5C%22%3E%20India%20uses%20the%20third%20generation%20of%20EVMs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20known%20as%20M3%20EVMs%2C%20which%20are%20designed%20to%20be%20tamper-proof.%20These%20machines%20enter%20a%20'Safety%20Mode'%20and%20become%20inoperable%20if%20any%20tampering%20attempts%20are%20detected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Union%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20countered%20Mr%20Musk's%20statement%20terming%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20sweeping%20generalisation%26quot%3B%20which%20holds%20no%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20huge%20sweeping%20generalisation%20statement%20that%20implies%20no%20one%20can%20build%20secure%20digital%20hardware.%20Wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20replied%20the%20former%20minister.%20%26quot%3BNo%20connectivity%2C%20no%20bluetooth%2C%20wifi%2C%20Internet%3B%20there%20is%20no%20way%20in.%20Factory-programmed%20controllers%20that%20cannot%20be%20reprogrammed.%20Electronic%20voting%20machines%20can%20be%20architected%20and%20built%20right%20as%20India%20has%20done.%20We%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20run%20a%20tutorial%2C%20Elon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20a%20huge%20sweeping%20generalization%20statement%20that%20implies%20no%20one%20can%20build%20secure%20digital%20hardware.%20Wrong.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40elonmusk%3C%2Fa%3E%20's%20view%20may%20apply%20to%20US%20n%20other%20places%20-%20where%20they%20use%20regular%20compute%20platforms%20to%20build%20Internet%20connected%20Voting%20machines.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnBut%20Indian%20EVMs%20are%20custom%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGiaCqU1n7O%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGiaCqU1n7O%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40RajeevRC_X)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRajeevRC_X%2Fstatus%2F1802195948254466461%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnything%20can%20be%20hacked%2C%26quot%3B%20replied%20Mr%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20dedicated%20team%20of%20professors%20from%20three%20prestigious%20Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Technology%20(IITs)%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20the%20latest%20upgrades%20of%20Indian%20EVMs.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20is%20supported%20by%20an%20eminent%20Technical%20Expert%20Committee%20(TEC)%20on%20EVMs%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20devices%20are%20robust%20and%20secure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftop-experts-from-iit-who-helped-design-indias-most-tamper-proof-evms-5728218%5C%22%3ETop%20Experts%20From%20IIT%20Who%20Helped%20Design%20India's%20Most%20Tamper-Proof%20EVMs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Dinesh%20K%20Sharma%2C%20a%20specialist%20in%20microelectronics%20and%20solid-state%20electronics%20from%20IIT%20Bombay%2C%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BIndian%20EVMs%20are%20different%20from%20other%20EVMs%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20M3%20EVMs%20have%20no%20connection%20to%20any%20other%20device%2C%20not%20even%20mains%20power%20supply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20this%20year%20addressed%20the%20issue%20of%20cross-verification%20of%20votes%20cast%20on%20EVMs%20through%20paper%20slips%20generated%20by%20Voter-Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%20machines.%20A%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%20rejected%20petitions%20seeking%20100%20per%20cent%20cross-verification%2C%20maintaining%20the%20current%20practice%20of%20verifying%20five%20randomly%20selected%20EVMs%20per%20Assembly%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-all-petitions-seeking-100-verification-of-vvpat-slips-during-elections-5526314%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBlindly%20Doubting%20System...%26quot%3B%3A%20Big%20Supreme%20Court%20Order%20On%20VVPAT%20Verification%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20court%20issued%20two%20directives%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20Firstly%2C%20after%20symbols%20are%20loaded%20into%20an%20EVM%2C%20the%20symbol%20loading%20unit%20must%20be%20sealed%20and%20secured%20in%20containers%20signed%20by%20the%20candidates%20and%20their%20representatives.%20Secondly%2C%20these%20sealed%20containers%2C%20along%20with%20the%20EVMs%2C%20should%20be%20kept%20in%20storerooms%20for%20at%20least%2045%20days%20after%20the%20declaration%20of%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718524980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Flrpu3os_elon-musk-rajeev-chandrasekhar_625x300_16_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwe-should-eliminate-evms-elon-musk-flags-risk-of-poll-rigging-5900100%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20chief%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20advised%20against%20the%20use%20of%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%2C%20citing%20concerns%20about%20their%20potential%20vulnerabilities%20to%20hacking.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwe-should-eliminate-evms-elon-musk-flags-risk-of-poll-rigging-5900100%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwe-should-eliminate-evms-elon-musk-flags-risk-of-poll-rigging-5900100%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwe-should-eliminate-evms-elon-musk-flags-risk-of-poll-rigging-5900100%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20Army%20announces%20'tactical%20pause'%20to%20increase%20flow%20of%20aid%20into%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718524213000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-04%2F27%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1714185150-3229.j