undraiser-with-obama-clooney-julia-roberts%2Famp_articleshow%2F111032799.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbiden-slams-supreme-court-at-28-million-fundraiser-with-obama-clooney-julia-roberts%2Famp_articleshow%2F111032799.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opposition's%20All-Out%20Attack%20On%20Centre%20Amid%20Nationwide%20NEET%20Protests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leaders%20have%20targeted%20the%20Centre%20over%20the%20massive%20row%20surrounding%20the%20National%20Eligibility-cum-Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)%20--%20an%20all-India%20examination%20for%20admission%20to%20medical%20courses%20--%20that%20has%20triggered%20protests%20by%20aspirants%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%2C%20which%20has%20been%20opposing%20NEET%20ever%20since%20it%20was%20introduced%2C%20has%20slammed%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20for%20destroying%20the%20exam's%20sanctity%20and%20said%20the%20Centre%20was%20a%20nothing%20more%20than%20a%20%26quot%3Bspectator%26quot%3B%20and%20backing%20coaching%20centres.%20The%20Congress%20has%20questioned%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20%26quot%3Bsilence%26quot%3B%20and%20demanded%20a%20Supreme%20Court-monitored%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResults%20for%20the%20medical%20entrance%20examination%2C%20which%20was%20taken%20by%2024%20lakh%20students%20on%20May%205%2C%20were%20declared%20on%20June%204%2C%20when%20counting%20of%20votes%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20was%20held.%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20results%2C%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leak%20surfaced.%20As%20many%20as%2067%20students%20scored%20the%20perfect%20score%20of%20720%2F720.%20The%20cut-off%20has%20gone%20up%20exponentially%2C%20leaving%20many%20wondering%20if%20they%20would%20get%20a%20medical%20college%20seat%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20issue%20that%20has%20come%20under%20the%20scanner%20is%20the%20award%20of%20grace%20marks%20to%20several%20students%20to%20compensate%20for%20loss%20of%20time%20at%20the%20exam%20centre.%20The%20protesting%20students%20allege%20this%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20inflated%20marks.%20The%20matter%20is%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20the%20Centre%20has%20told%20the%20court%20that%20it%20had%20cancelled%20the%20grace%20marks%20given%20to%201%2C563%20candidates.%20They%20now%20have%20the%20option%20to%20take%20a%20re-test%20or%20forgo%20the%20grace%20marks.%20But%20a%20section%20of%20students%20has%20said%20this%20is%20not%20enough%20and%20the%20exam%20must%20be%20repeated%20for%20all%20students.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEducation%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20has%20said%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20of%20paper%20leak%20and%20claims%20of%20corruption%20in%20NTA%20are%20unfounded.%C2%A0%26quot%3BAll%20the%20facts%20related%20to%20this%20are%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20are%20under%20consideration.%20The%20kind%20of%20politics%20being%20done%20on%20this%20issue%20is%20only%20an%20attempt%20to%20spread%20confusion%20and%20it%20affects%20the%20mental%20peace%20of%20the%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pradhan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20Centre%20over%20the%20raging%20issue%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20grace%20marks%20are%20not%20the%20only%20problem.%20%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20rigging%2C%20papers%20have%20been%20leaked%2C%20and%20corruption%20has%20taken%20place.%20The%20future%20of%2024%20lakh%20students%20appearing%20in%20the%20NEET%20examination%20is%20at%20stake%20due%20to%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bscam%20in%20NEET%26quot%3B%20has%20devastated%20more%20than%2024%20lakh%20students%20and%20their%20families.%20The%20Opposition%20party's%20general%20secretary%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20has%20said%20the%20Education%20Minister's%20%26quot%3Barrogant%20response%26quot%3B%20ignores%20the%20cries%20of%2024%20lakh%20students%20and%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20INDIA%20allies%20have%20also%20joined%20the%20protest%20against%20the%20exam.%20RJD%20leader%20and%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20Bihar%20Assembly%20Tejasjwi%20Yadav%20said%20paper%20leaks%20are%20%26quot%3Binevitable%26quot%3B%20whenever%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20or%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20leader%20and%20Bengal%20education%20minister%20Bratya%20Basu%20said%20the%20Centre%20expedites%20a%20probe%20into%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20teachers'%20recruitment%20in%20the%20eastern%20state.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20is%20silent%20on%20probing%20the%20irregularities%20in%20NEET-UG%2C%20which%20affected%20the%20future%20careers%20of%20lakhs%20of%20aspiring%20doctors%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECounselling%20for%20seats%20in%20medical%20colleges%20begins%20on%20July%206%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20resume%20its%20hearing%20in%20the%20matter%20on%20July%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718514060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ffm3so5b8_neet-protest_625x300_16_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-row-oppositions-all-out-attack-on-centre-amid-nationwide-neet-protests-5900471%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opposition%20leaders%20have%20targeted%20the%20Centre%20over%20the%20massive%20row%20surrounding%20the%20National%20Eligibility-cum-Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)%20--%20an%20all-India%20examination%20for%20admission%20to%20medical%20courses%20--%20that%20has%20triggered%20protests%20by%20aspirants%20in%20several%20areas%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-row-oppositions-all-out-attack-on-centre-amid-nationwide-neet-protests-5900471%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.o