20to%20start%20growing%20them%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Eyyo%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296470%2Faward-winning-kerala-terrace-farmer-grows-seasonal-veggies-zucchini-cauliflower%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrow%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20typically%20used%20for%20indoor%20farming%2C%20the%20septuagenarian%20decided%20to%20try%20them%20outdoors.%20His%20initial%20experiments%20with%20traditional%20plastic%20grow%20bags%20were%20unsatisfactory.%20Concurrently%2C%20he%20was%20concerned%20about%20the%20rampant%20disposal%20of%20plastic%20bottles.%20This%20led%20him%20to%20wonder%20%E2%80%94%20could%20a%20plastic%20bottle%20be%20used%20to%20water%20his%20plants%20slowly%2C%20mimicking%20a%20drip%20irrigation%20system%3F%20The%20answer%20he%20discovered%20was%20a%20resounding%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20initially%20began%20by%20modifying%20traditional%20plastic%20grow%20bags%2C%20making%20holes%20to%20add%20water.%20However%2C%20these%20bags%20didn%E2%80%99t%20last%20long.%20After%20months%20of%20trials%2C%20he%20found%20his%20solution%20in%20silpaulin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20durable%2C%20waterproof%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eyyo%20with%20his%20patented%20grow%20bag%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2