20very%20important%20due%20to%20the%20rich%20history%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehaveli%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecounting%20the%20fascinating%20story%2C%20Paramveer%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20story%20dates%20back%20approximately%20500%20years%2C%20rooted%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Sirohi%2C%20which%20is%20around%2050%20km%20from%20my%20current%20home.%20My%20ancestors%20lived%20in%20that%20area%2C%20and%20in%20those%20times%2C%20it%20was%20common%20to%20leave%20one%E2%80%99s%20place%20and%20fight%20to%20secure%20and%20travel%20across%20lands%20on%20the%20Maharaja%E2%80%99s%20instructions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20notable%20ancestor%20of%20Paramveer%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F94978%2Fudaipur-elderlycare-india-governmentsupport%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresided%20in%20Udaipur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20near%20the%20picturesque%20Pichola%20Lake%2C%20on%20a%20hill%20known%20as%20Haridas%20Ji%20Ki%20Makri%E2%80%94%E2%80%99Malri%E2%80%99%20meaning%20a%20small%20hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20lived%20there%20with%20his%20army.%20The%20Maharana%20of%20Udaipur%20had%20issues%20with%20a%20troublesome%20tribe%20in%20the%20area%20where%20we%20now%20live%2C%20in%20Bisalpur.%20This%20area%20was%20on%20the%20border%20between%20Jodhpur%20and%20Udaipur%20at%20that%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Maharana%20instructed%20my%20ancestor%2C%20Rao%20Haridasi%2C%20to%20suppress%20these%20rivals.%20He%20successfully%20conquered%20the%20land%2C%20and%20in%201705%2C%20this%20territory%2C%20comprising%2024%20villages%2C%20was%20granted%20to%20my%20family%2C%20making%20us%20direct%20subjects%20of%20the%20Maharana.%20Since%20then%2C%20from%201705%20onwards%2C%20my%20family%20has%20resided%20in%20this%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20of%20the%20property%20has%20evolved%20over%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%